title: Speed finals | Villars 2024
description:
The 2024 IFSC Climbing and Paraclimbing European Championships is scheduled to take place in Villars, Switzerland, from 24 August to 1 September. Climbers from all over the continent will compete in Boulder, Lead, Speed, and Boulder & Lead.
